records.name: Gangehi Island Resort & Spa

descriptions.direction: Located in Gangehi Island, Gangehi Island Resort is on the beach. Mathiveri Ferry Terminal and Mathiveri Harbor are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Ukulhas Beach and Sunset Beach. Mathiveri Finolhu and Folhudhoo Harbor are two other places to visit that come recommended.
